longBusinessSummary: Matachewan Consolidated Mines, Limited invests in various petroleum interests and mineral properties in Canada. It holds 50% interest in 8 mining leases located in Hislop and Guibord Townships near Matheson, Ontario; and a royalty interest in the Matachewan property, which comprise 24 mining claims in the Young Davidson mine located in Powell and Cairo Townships near Matachewan Area, Ontario. The company was incorporated in 1933 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
